  "_comment": "Template for the update manifest. Copy to the ROOT of the Oztrk4/AOCom GitHub repo as `update.json` (main branch) each time you release. `signature` is the FULL CONTENTS of the .sig file that `npm run tauri build` generates next to the installer (requires TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY to be set). `url` points at the installer you uploaded as a GitHub Release asset. `version` must be higher than the installed app's version for the prompt to appear.",
